  "original_title": "\u0b90\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bb0\u0ba3 \u0ba4\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bc8 ! - 22 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Six sentenced to death for shooting five - Judgment after 22 years of trial",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Matara High Court today (30) sentenced 6 persons to death for the murder of five persons. Matara High Court Judge Tamara Tennakoon announced the verdict.",
        "On November 14, 2000, 5 people who were going to a case related to murder charges were shot and killed near Mathara - Thevinuvara vicarage.",
        "The Attorney General has filed a case against 15 persons in the Matara High Court in connection with this incident.",
        "In this case, the trial is set to begin today, 22 years after the incident.",
        "Of the 15 accused, four died during the trial and five were acquitted by a court today. Six convicts were sentenced to death."
      ],
